T02TD1966E:105b-0: @105b `/ 'chi bdag yi dags rgyal po'i sgrub thabs bzhugs /
T02TD1966E:105b-2: # // 'chi bdag yi dags rgyal po ni //
T02TD1966E:105b-3: 'chi bdag bdud ces bya ba ste //
T02TD1966E:105b-4: 'gro ba kun gyi lus kyi bdud //
T02TD1966E:105b-5: lus dang grib ma'i tshul bzhin du //
T02TD1966E:105b-6: 'gro ba kun la snang ba ste //
T02TD1966E:105b-7: phung po nying mtshams sbyor ba po //
T02TD1966E:105b-8: 'jigs pa de yi gzugs mthong na //
T02TD1966E:105b-9: ya ma de yi dring na 'byung //
T02TD1966E:105b-10: de nas rang gi srog gi bdud //
T02TD1966E:105b-11: lhag pa'i phyogs na gnas pa ste //
T02TD1966E:105b-12: gtsigs pa can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1966E:105b-13: de la 'chi bdag skyes bu'i gzugs //
T02TD1966E:105b-14: khru gang yi dags gos la bri //
T02TD1966E:105b-15: nag po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD1966E:105b-16: 'jigs pa ral pa mche bzhi gtsigs //
T02TD1966E:105b-17: rgyan med rus pa'i phreng ba can //
T02TD1966E:105b-18: g-yas pa ya ma'i dbyug pa 'dzin //
T02TD1966E:105b-19: sdigs mdzub zhags pa g-yon na bsnams //
T02TD1966E:105b-20: ma he dag la gnas pa bri //
T02TD1966E:105b-21: de la rnal 'byor chen po yi //
T02TD1966E:105b-22: mdun du gnas la zhi gnas bya //
T02TD1966E:105b-23: yang na sam sa dhi rnam gsum las //
T02TD1966E:105b-24: h'um las nag po chen po ste //
T02TD1966E:105b-25: yi ge bcu gcig brjod byas la //
T02TD1966E:105b-26: ras la bris pa bzhin du bsgom //
T02TD1966E:105b-27: aom k'a la r'u pa ya ma r'a dza h'um phat /
T02TD1966E:105b-28: de nas bsnyen pa bya ba gsungs //
T02TD1966E:105b-29: dur khrod nags tshal song byas la //
T02TD1966E:105b-30: bzlas brjod byas pa'i tshul dag gis //
T02TD1966E:105b-31: ha ha bzhad cing 'ong bar rigs //
T02TD1966E:105b-32: mngon du gyur nas ba lim sbyin //
T02TD1966E:105b-33: de la bsnyen pa'i snying po 'di'o //
T02TD1966E:105b-34: aom k'a la r'u pa bh'i ma yaksha h'um /
T02TD1966E:105b-37: sarba bh'u ta aa dhi pa ta ye /
T02TD1966E:105b-38: ya ma r'a dza ya h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1966E:105b-39: thog ma dbus mtha' yang dag ldan /
T02TD1966E:105b-40: bcu bzhi phye ba bsnyen pa yin //
T02TD1966E:105b-41: rim pa bzhin du ma bye ba //
T02TD1966E:105b-42: nye ba'i bsnyen pa yin par shes //
T02TD1966E:105b-43: grub ste mngon du gyur pa na //
T02TD1966E:105b-44: sha chen gtor ma chen po sbyin /
T02TD1966E:105b-45: aom k'a la r'u pa ya ma r'a dza h'um ai dam ba lim grihna kha kha kh'a hi kh'a hi /
T02TD1966E:105b-46: tshogs la sogs pa mngon du sbyin //
T02TD1966E:105b-47: de ltar grub na las bya ste //
T02TD1966E:105b-48: bhanbha mtshan ngan bzang po btsal //
T02TD1966E:105b-49: dum bu gcig gam gnyis pa la //
T02TD1966E:105b-50: dpral ba'i ngos nas ltag par drang //
T02TD1966E:105b-51: mi thod dag pa ro ras la //
T02TD1966E:106a-2: snag tsha bya rog khrag dang ni //
T02TD1966E:106a-3: dur khrod sol ba bong bu'i chus //
T02TD1966E:106a-4: mi rkang snyu gus legs par bri //
T02TD1966E:106a-5: spyi bo'i ngos kyi phyogs dag la //
T02TD1966E:106a-6: ras la 'khor lo bri bar bya //
T02TD1966E:106a-7: rim pa skor gsum ldan pa la //
T02TD1966E:106a-8: rim pa gnyis pa dag la ni //
T02TD1966E:106a-9: rtsibs gnyis gnyis kyi tshad la bri //
T02TD1966E:106a-10: de la gsang sngags dgod pa ni //
T02TD1966E:106a-11: ma ma sha tr'um aa mu kam /
T02TD1966E:106a-12: 'khor lo lte ba'i dbus su bri //
T02TD1966E:106a-13: shar nas brtsams nas 'di lta ste //
T02TD1966E:106a-14: tr'a sa ya tr'a sa ya //
T02TD1966E:106a-16: sho sha ya sho sha ya /
T02TD1966E:106a-22: rim pa tha ma dag la ni //
T02TD1966E:106a-23: shar nas brtsams nas 'di ltar bri //
T02TD1966E:106a-24: tsaksha badzra gho ra ba tra ma kshe tra p'a la ya /
T02TD1966E:106a-29: aom m'a ra ya badzra ye stam bha ya h'um phat /
T02TD1966E:106a-30: bar du dgra yi ming rus bri //
T02TD1966E:106a-31: rgyab srubs dag la gsang sngags bri //
T02TD1966E:106a-32: skud pa sngon po nag po yis //
T02TD1966E:106a-33: thod pa de ni bsdam par bya //
T02TD1966E:106a-34: ro shing me la bhandha bsro //
T02TD1966E:106a-35: de la zhag gsum byas nas kyang //
T02TD1966E:106a-36: las kyi 'chi bdag khru gang la //
T02TD1966E:106a-37: zhal gcig mche gtsigs phyag gnyis pa //
T02TD1966E:106a-38: bdun por sa dang rnam snang dang //
T02TD1966E:106a-39: dur khrod sol ba'i rgyu dag la //
T02TD1966E:106a-40: bong bu'i chu yis gzugs byas te //
T02TD1966E:106a-41: de yi snying gar thod pa gzhug /'khor lo la bris sngags bzlas te //
T02TD1966E:106a-42: mar tshes bcu bzhi dang brgyad la //
T02TD1966E:106a-43: dur khrod ro khang dag tu mnan //
T02TD1966E:106a-44: de ltar las ni rdzogs gyur nas //
T02TD1966E:106a-45: gang la bya ba'i dngos po de //
T02TD1966E:106a-46: rang gi bdud kyi dbang du gyur //
T02TD1966E:106a-47: 'chi bdag yi dags rgyal po de //
T02TD1966E:106a-48: ma dros mtshe yi 'bri dkyil la //
T02TD1966E:106a-49: ri nag po yi pha mtha' ste //
T02TD1966E:106a-50: spos dang ri bo'i bar dag na //
T02TD1966E:106a-51: chu dang zheng du cha mnyam mtsho //
T02TD1966E:106a-53: 'chi bdag yi dags rgyal po'i gnas //
T02TD1966E:106a-54: 'gro ba'i ltag pa'i phyogs na gnas //
T02TD1966E:106a-55: de yi yum de tsa mund'i //
T02TD1966E:106a-56: rabs chad pho mo'i thod pa la //
T02TD1966E:106a-57: ya gnyis dag gi bar du yang //
T02TD1966E:106a-58: ro ras dag la gzugs bri ba //
T02TD1966E:106a-59: zhal dang phyag zhabs sngon bzhin bri //
T02TD1966E:106a-61: nag mo mig gsum khro gnyer can //
T02TD1966E:106a-62: kha gdangs skra ba rdzes nu ma 'phyang //
T02TD1966E:106a-63: gsus chen dus 'gro'i gos gyon ma //
T02TD1966E:106b-0: g-yas na tri sh'ul g-yon thod @106b pa //
T02TD1966E:106b-1: mi yi thod pa dang sbyar ba //
T02TD1966E:106b-2: mi yi rgyus pas bsdams pa yi //
T02TD1966E:106b-3: bar du 'khor lo gzhug par bya //
T02TD1966E:106b-5: snga ma bzhin du bri bar bya //
T02TD1966E:106b-6: de la ma mo'i 'khor lo ni //
T02TD1966E:106b-7: ras la 'chi bdag tshul bzhin du //
T02TD1966E:106b-8: rtsibs brgyad gnyis dang ldan pa la //
T02TD1966E:106b-9: dbus nas brtsams te de bzhin bri //
T02TD1966E:106b-11: lte ba'i dbus su bri bar bya //
T02TD1966E:106b-12: shar nas rim pa 'di bzhin du //
T02TD1966E:106b-17: pra ma tha pra ma tha /
T02TD1966E:106b-21: rim pa tha ma dag la ni //
T02TD1966E:106b-22: shar nas brtsams nas 'di lta ste //
T02TD1966E:106b-23: ni ga na shi bam ham yam ri tshu sa ya /
T02TD1966E:106b-26: tshinda ma de pa shi gam m'a ra ya n'a sha ya h'um phat /
T02TD1966E:106b-27: 'khor lo gnyis kyi bar du yang //
T02TD1966E:106b-28: gang la bya ba'i ming gzugs gzhug / bla mas 'chi bdag bsams byas te //
T02TD1966E:106b-29: srog gi snying po bzlas par bya //
T02TD1966E:106b-30: gos sngon gyon pa de bzhin du //
T02TD1966E:106b-31: yum mam las mkhan dpa' bo bzhin //
T02TD1966E:106b-32: yum gyi srog snying bcu po dgod //
T02TD1966E:106b-33: aom hr'i: tsa mundh'i ye h'um phat sv'a h'a //
T02TD1966E:106b-34: yab yum 'khor lo gang yin pa //
T02TD1966E:106b-35: gong gi thod par gzhug par bya //
T02TD1966E:106b-36: shi ba'i skra yi skud pa la //
T02TD1966E:106b-37: mi rgyus dag gi skud pas bsdams //
T02TD1966E:106b-38: mi yi rgyu mas gzungs thag byas //
T02TD1966E:106b-39: gtso dang gzungs kyis gzung byas nas //
T02TD1966E:106b-40: mandala steng bzhag bzlas pa bya //
T02TD1966E:106b-42: gtso dang gzugs kyi 'bum phrag bzlas //
T02TD1966E:106b-43: de nas bzlas pa rdzogs nas kyang //
T02TD1966E:106b-44: dur khrod lha khang ro khang ngam //
T02TD1966E:106b-45: lha klu drag po'i gnas su mnan //
T02TD1966E:106b-46: lha la sogs pa shi bar bstan /
T02TD1966E:106b-47: de yi sgrub pa'i gnas rnams kyang //
T02TD1966E:106b-48: dben pa'i gnas su byas nas ni //
T02TD1966E:106b-49: bla ma pha ma mchod pa yin //
T02TD1966E:106b-50: gang byung yang ni bsgral ba yin //
T02TD1966E:106b-51: de tshe bsgral ba ma byas na //
T02TD1966E:106b-53: gsang ba gzhan la bstan mi bya //
T02TD1966E:106b-54: 'chi bdag yi dags rgyal po'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
